{"tid":1394960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[遍地開花] 到一班香港體育記者有說話想同大家講","createTime":"2019-08-01T15:04:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T03:14:01.000Z","uid":110067,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d9f09cd37574c918592a1cb62ae6048bcd4ee59c","tid":1394960,"uid":110067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:04:44.000Z","msg":"代朋友開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n------------------<br />\n致 香港人：<br />\n<br />\n我們是香港體育記者，向來在體育圈有種說法「體育不談政治」，但目前的香港局勢讓我們不得不正視香港的問題。自送中條例修訂風波開始，港府一直漠視民意，導致超過二百萬巿民上街遊行，加上警方多次超越警權範圍對付示威者，令抗爭行動愈演愈烈，社會出現嚴重撕裂，除了巿民人身安全受到威脅，民生亦受到嚴重影響。<br />\n<br />\n香港一群精英運動員日前已發聲要求港府早日回應大眾訴求。香港運動員多年來披著區旗，經常在外地比賽，屢獲佳績，為港爭光，我們不時報道香港運動員拿獎牌的消息，均以身為香港人而感到光榮及自豪。但如今距離明年東京奧運不足一年，香港的不穩現況已影響運動員的備戰情緒。<br />\n<br />\n作為香港體育記者的我們，雖不像港聞記者般要走上「戰場」前線，但我們在工作中依然緊記作為記者應有的新聞操守，保持政治中立，報道事實之真相及全部，奈何警方在鎮壓示威行動中，屢次毆打、驅趕記者，更甚是港聞記者在採訪工作期間，遭到警務人員以涉嫌煽動暴亂罪而要求停止採訪及檢查身份文件。<br />\n<br />\n為此，我們均認為要全力支持前線港聞記者，強烈譴責警方嚴重阻礙新聞採訪自由，並要求港府盡快回應市民訴求，包括成立獨立委員會調查事件原因，明確要求保持新聞採訪自由，令香港能早日回復平靜和諧。<br />\n<br />\n當我們放下紙筆、放下相機時，我們都是香港人，讓我們一起撐港隊，撐香港。<br />\n<br />\n一群愛香港、全力支持運動員的體育記者上<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EVB29Uz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEVB29Uz.jpg&h=04263ec9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vo6VLsZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvo6VLsZ.jpg&h=8cc130f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b7gKDN3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb7gKDN3.jpg&h=61e724d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P70SNGt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP70SNGt.jpg&h=ef50dfa4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uPfSNGz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuPfSNGz.jpg&h=13dbf8c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ixXazmE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FixXazmE.jpg&h=11d5b179&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RCDXYOq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRCDXYOq.jpg&h=46540639&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/trPTw8w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtrPTw8w.jpg&h=af20d141&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KZ8EsG9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKZ8EsG9.jpg&h=e0dfc4c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g8ArR84.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg8ArR84.jpg&h=c5d3d6e6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd514f9abfacb59eac540b4cf50e645d7359906d","tid":1394960,"uid":254860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:09:46.000Z","msg":"五大訴求!<br />\n光復香港 時代革命!"},{"pid":"e0d7dd8f4784d74055acecee5ceb25ed008440c2","tid":1394960,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:10:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9ab162535638f67c8f1d1b18f585b0e494e4202","tid":1394960,"uid":95221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:10:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />we connect"},{"pid":"49ea421f34fd2d2bc7d47082c7a06a1f210aa72a","tid":1394960,"uid":17683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:10:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45239086717e04df2d88852784e90429a54dc278","tid":1394960,"uid":183120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:20:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff796f42bd354ce6897b8f1af3f23e32eace6bc5","tid":1394960,"uid":132889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c